# DBS Check Expiry Reminder

This is a lightweight Google Apps Script tool designed to help tutoring businesses or educational organizations monitor the expiry of DBS (Disclosure and Barring Service) certificates stored in a Google Sheet. It automatically checks certificate issue dates, flags those nearing or past expiry, and sends email reminders or reports.

## ‚ú® Features

- ‚úÖ Automatically parses DBS issue dates from a Google Sheet
- ‚úÖ Flags certificates nearing expiry (11+ months old) or expired (12+ months old)
- ‚úÖ Sends internal email alerts or tutor reminders (if email addresses are available)
- ‚úÖ Generates on-demand or scheduled reports
- ‚úÖ Built entirely in Google Apps Script (no hosting or external services required)

## üìÅ Google Sheet Format

Your sheet should have at least the following columns:

| Name        | DBS Issue Date |
|-------------|----------------|
| Jane Smith  | 2023-06-28

